---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("April 6 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Move-Out Cleaning for Huntsville Landlords"
  description={isPublished ? "Huntsville property managers: the exact move-out cleaning checklist to turn rentals fast. Madison County standards, pricing & how to vet your cleaning vendor." : "Coming Soon: Move-Out Cleaning Requirements for Huntsville Property Managers"}
  ogImage="https://thevalleycleanteam.com/og-image.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Move-Out Cleaning Requirements for Huntsville Property Managers"
    description="Huntsville property managers: Learn the exact move-out cleaning requirements needed to prep rentals for new tenants quickly and maintain high property standards."
    publishDate="April 6 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Move-Out/Real Estate
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Move-Out Cleaning Requirements for Huntsville Property Managers
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming April 6 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>April 6 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- DIRECT ANSWER BLOCK - Critical for AEO -->
        <div
          class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985] p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg"
        >
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-0">
            <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Move-out cleaning requirements for
            Huntsville property managers center on a thorough, checklist-driven
            clean that goes well beyond everyday tidying—carpet and floor care,
            full kitchen and bathroom detailing, dusting of every surface, and
            streak-free windows. Meeting these standards protects property
            value, speeds tenant turnover, and keeps each unit move-in ready.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          What Are the Move-Out Cleaning Requirements for Huntsville Property
          Managers?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          In Huntsville, property managers face unique challenges when it comes
          to move-out cleaning. Restoring apartments, condos, and homes to a
          condition suitable for new residents requires a systematic approach.
          Here's what you need to know to meet and exceed these expectations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Understanding Basic Move-Out Cleaning Standards
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          For property managers in Huntsville, adhering to a comprehensive
          <a
            href="/services/move-in-out-cleaning"
            class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline">move-out cleaning</a
          > checklist is crucial. These standards uphold the property's reputation
          and ensure compliance with local regulations and tenant agreements.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Carpet and floor cleaning:</strong> Carpets should be
            professionally cleaned to remove stains and odors. Hard floors
            require mopping and polishing.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Kitchen detailing:</strong> Every appliance, from ovens to
            refrigerators, must be spotless. Cabinets, counters, and sinks
            should be degreased and sanitized.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Bathroom sanitation:</strong> Tubs, showers, toilets, and
            sinks need thorough scrubbing with disinfectants. Tiles and grout
            should be immaculate.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Dusting and surface cleaning:</strong> All surfaces,
            including baseboards, ceiling fans, and light fixtures, should be
            dust-free.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Window and glass polishing:</strong> Windows should be
            cleaned inside and out, ensuring streak-free glass and spotless
            sills.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          The Importance of Military-Precision in Cleaning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          At The Valley Clean Team, we understand the importance of precision
          cleaning, especially for move-out scenarios. Our veteran-owned team
          brings a disciplined, meticulous approach to every project, using
          military-style checklists to guarantee nothing is overlooked.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          This level of attention to detail is crucial in Huntsville, where
          property standards are high and tenant turnover can be frequent. By
          maintaining rigorous cleaning protocols, property managers can ensure
          that each new tenant steps into a pristine, welcoming environment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Benefits of Professional Move-Out Cleaning Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Investing in a professional cleaning service like The Valley Clean
          Team offers significant advantages:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Time efficiency:</strong> Free up your schedule by letting
            us handle the comprehensive cleaning tasks.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Guaranteed results:</strong> Our services come with a
            satisfaction guarantee, ensuring properties meet or exceed standard
            requirements.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Enhanced property value:</strong> Well-maintained properties
            attract higher-quality tenants and can justify premium rental rates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Local expertise:</strong> Our familiarity with Huntsville's
            property landscape ensures we meet local expectations and
            regulations.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Tailoring Cleaning Plans for Different Property Types
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Different properties require tailored cleaning approaches. Whether
          managing a compact downtown apartment or a sprawling suburban home,
          our team adjusts the scope of work accordingly. For units that haven't
          been maintained regularly, a
          <a
            href="/services/deep-cleaning"
            class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline">deep clean</a
          > may be the right fit. This customized strategy ensures all unique features
          of a property are addressed, providing uniform quality across your portfolio.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          For instance, high-traffic areas in larger homes may need additional
          attention, while smaller units might focus on maximizing space through
          strategic cleaning techniques. Our exacting standards ensure every
          square inch is properly cared for.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How to Prepare for a Move-Out Cleaning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Preparation is key to a successful move-out clean. Here's how property
          managers can facilitate the process:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Clear the space:</strong> Ensure all personal belongings are
            removed to allow full access to cleaning areas.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Document existing conditions:</strong> Take photos of any
            pre-existing damage or wear to avoid disputes with tenants.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Schedule in advance:</strong> Book your cleaning service
            ahead of time to secure your preferred date, especially during peak
            moving seasons.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- CLOSING CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Reclaim Your Time—Book The Valley Clean Team Today
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Stop worrying about the meticulous details of move-out cleaning. Our
            veteran-owned, precision-driven team is ready to keep your Huntsville
            properties turn-ready. Get your free quote now.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="tel:2568261100"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
            >
              <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Call 256-826-1100
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition"
            >
              Request Quote Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">April 6 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
  <!-- Huntsville Services CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#FFA985]/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Move-Out Cleaning Services in Huntsville, AL
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
        The Valley Clean Team helps Huntsville property managers and tenants pass
        inspections with thorough, checklist-driven move-out cleans.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/locations/huntsville"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#FFA985] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
        >
          View Huntsville Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/locations/huntsville/move-out-cleaning/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[#FFA985] text-[#FFA985] font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#FFA985] hover:text-white transition"
        >
          Get a Move-Out Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
